"Family" = "家庭版";
"Education" = "教育版";
"Business" = "商業版";
"At-risk grant" = "互助許可";

/* License verdict notes */
"Paste your license key first." = "請先貼上你的許可證金鑰。";
"Couldn't read the license input." = "無法讀取輸入的許可證。";
"Activated. Thank you for supporting Farewell." = "已啟用。感謝你支援 Farewell。";
"No license installed." = "未安裝任何許可證。";
"This key isn’t valid for this build (wrong key, or the key was altered)." = "此金鑰對該版本無效（金鑰錯誤，或金鑰已被篡改）。";
"This license is for a different major version of Farewell." = "此許可證適用於 Farewell 的其他主版本。";
"This license isn’t authorized for this Mac. A free re-issue is available — see farewell.pro/license-policy." = "此許可證未授權用於此 Mac。可免費重新簽發——請參閱 farewell.pro/license-policy。";
"That doesn’t look like a valid license key." = "這看起來不是有效的許可證金鑰。";
"Couldn’t verify (couldn’t read this Mac’s serial number)." = "無法驗證（無法讀取此 Mac 的序列號）。";
"Unknown license state." = "許可證狀態未知。";

/* --- Create-vault form --- */
"New vault path (…/my.vault)" = "新保險庫路徑（…/my.vault）";
"Capacity" = "容量";
"size" = "大小";
"MB" = "MB";
"Choose any size you want (e.g. 64, 512, 4096…). The vault file is always exactly this size on disk, no matter how much you store — that's part of the deniability." = "選擇任意你想要的大小（例如 64、512、4096…）。無論你儲存多少，保險庫檔案在磁碟上始終正好佔用此大小——這是可否認性的一部分。";
"Generated (recommended)" = "生成的（推薦）";
"My own" = "我自己的";
"There is no recovery, and there is no self-destruct: the file looks like random data and your passphrase is the ONLY thing protecting it. That is why it must be strong — and why you must not lose it." = "沒有恢復，也沒有自毀：檔案看起來像隨機資料，而你的密碼短語是唯一保護它的東西。因此它必須足夠強——也因此你絕不能丟失它。";
"Also require a YubiKey (hardware key)" = "同時要求 YubiKey（硬體金鑰）";
"YubiKey PIN (leave blank if none)" = "YubiKey PIN 碼（若無則留空）";
"Also enrol a backup key now" = "現在同時註冊一個備份金鑰";
"You'll enrol the keys one at a time: insert the first key and touch it, then swap to the second when asked. Either key will open the vault — keep the backup somewhere safe and separate." = "你將逐個註冊金鑰：插入第一個金鑰並輕觸，然後在提示時換上第二個。任一金鑰都能開啟保險庫——請將備份金鑰儲存在安全且獨立的地方。";
"You'll be asked to TOUCH the key to enrol it. Then a copy of this vault can't be brute-forced without the physical key. Lose your only key and the vault is gone — there is no recovery, so a backup key is recommended." = "系統會要求你輕觸金鑰以完成註冊。之後，沒有實體金鑰就無法暴力破解此保險庫的副本。若丟失唯一的金鑰，保險庫將無法找回——沒有恢復，因此建議設定備份金鑰。";
"Record my identity in this vault" = "在此保險庫中記錄我的身份";
"Stores “%@” inside the encrypted vault — visible only after unlock. ⚠︎ This ATTRIBUTES the vault to you if it is ever decrypted. Leave OFF if you need deniability." = "將「%@」儲存在加密保險庫內——僅在解鎖後可見。⚠︎ 一旦保險庫被解密，這會將其歸屬於你。如果你需要可否認性，請保持關閉。";
"Activate a license first to record your identity." = "請先啟用許可證以記錄你的身份。";
"Create and open" = "建立並開啟";
"Creating a vault needs an active license. Activate one with “Manage license…” below. (Opening existing vaults always works.)" = "建立保險庫需要有效的許可證。請透過下方的「管理許可證…」啟用一個。（開啟現有保險庫始終可用。）";
"Choose where to save the vault (Choose…)." = "選擇保險庫的儲存位置（「選擇…」）。";
"Generate a passphrase." = "生成一個密碼短語。";
"Tick the box confirming you saved the passphrase." = "勾選核取方塊以確認你已儲存密碼短語。";
"Enter a passphrase." = "輸入一個密碼短語。";
"Passphrases don't match." = "兩個密碼短語不一致。";
"Passphrase must reach “Very strong” (4/4)." = "密碼短語必須達到「非常強」（4/4）。";
"Regenerate" = "重新生成";
"≈ 129 bits — 10 random words" = "≈ 129 位 — 10 個隨機單詞";
"I have written this passphrase down somewhere safe" = "我已將此密碼短語記在安全的地方";
"Confirm passphrase" = "確認密碼短語";
"Must reach “Very strong” (4/4). Tip: 5+ random, unrelated words beat any short clever password." = "必須達到「非常強」（4/4）。提示：5 個以上互不相關的隨機單詞勝過任何簡短而巧妙的密碼。";
"Choose Folder" = "選擇資料夾";
"Choose the folder for the new vault. You'll set its name back in the Farewell window. An existing vault is never overwritten." = "為新保險庫選擇資料夾。你將在 Farewell 視窗中設定其名稱。現有保險庫絕不會被覆蓋。";

/* --- Error messages (humanError) --- */
"OK (unexpected)" = "好（意外）";
"Invalid argument" = "引數無效";
"Not found" = "未找到";
"Couldn't read the vault file (missing or unreadable)." = "無法讀取保險庫檔案（缺失或不可讀）。";
"This vault is already open in another window or process." = "此保險庫已在另一個視窗或程序中開啟。";
"Vault has been wiped — contents unrecoverable" = "保險庫已被擦除——內容無法恢復";
"Couldn't open it. Check the passphrase — and, if this vault uses a YubiKey, that it's plugged in and you entered its PIN." = "無法開啟。請檢查密碼短語——如果此保險庫使用 YubiKey，請檢查它已插入且你已輸入其 PIN 碼。";
"Vault header has been tampered with" = "保險庫標頭已被篡改";
"Counter rollback detected" = "檢測到計數器回滾";
"Passphrase too weak — use a stronger or generated one" = "密碼短語太弱——請使用更強的或生成的密碼短語";
"No YubiKey detected — plug it in and try again." = "未檢測到 YubiKey——請插入後重試。";
"YubiKey check failed — wrong PIN, or it wasn't touched in time." = "YubiKey 檢查失敗——PIN 碼錯誤，或未及時輕觸。";
"More than one key is plugged in. With a PIN, please leave only the key you're unlocking with plugged in (trying a PIN on the wrong key can lock it), then try again." = "插入了多個金鑰。使用 PIN 碼時，請僅保留你要用來解鎖的那個金鑰（在錯誤的金鑰上嘗試 PIN 碼可能將其鎖定），然後重試。";
"Not a Farewell vault file" = "不是 Farewell 保險庫檔案";
"Vault uses a format this build cannot read" = "保險庫使用了此版本無法讀取的格式";

/* --- Keys-management panel --- */
"Keys" = "金鑰";
"Hardware-key management." = "硬體金鑰管理。";
"Vault passphrase" = "保險庫密碼短語";
"Current key's PIN (leave blank if no PIN or no key)" = "當前金鑰的 PIN 碼（若無 PIN 碼或無金鑰則留空）";
"Cancel" = "取消";
"Show keys" = "顯示金鑰";
"Reading keys…" = "正在讀取金鑰…";
"Done" = "完成";
"Passphrase-only — no hardware key enrolled." = "僅密碼短語——未註冊任何硬體金鑰。";
"Only one key opens this vault. **Lose it and the vault is gone forever — there is no recovery.** Enrol a backup key below so either key works." = "只有一個金鑰能開啟此保險庫。**丟失它，保險庫將永遠丟失——沒有恢復。** 請在下方註冊一個備份金鑰，使兩個金鑰都可用。";
"Key %lld" = "金鑰 %lld";
"Remove (last)" = "移除（最後一個）";
"Revoke" = "吊銷";
"Revoke this key?" = "吊銷此金鑰？";
"It will no longer open this vault; the other keys still will. Revoking uses only your passphrase, then you'll touch a remaining key once to reopen the vault." = "它將不再開啟此保險庫；其他金鑰仍可使用。吊銷僅使用你的密碼短語，然後你將輕觸一個剩餘金鑰一次以重新開啟保險庫。";
"Remove your last key?" = "移除你的最後一個金鑰？";
"Remove last key" = "移除最後一個金鑰";
"This turns the vault back into passphrase-only: the passphrase alone will open it, and opening becomes slower again (by design). Insert the key now — you'll touch it once so it can be safely removed." = "這會將保險庫恢復為僅密碼短語模式：僅憑密碼短語即可開啟，而開啟會再次變慢（出於設計）。現在請插入金鑰——你將輕觸它一次，以便安全地移除它。";
"Add a hardware key" = "新增硬體金鑰";
"Add a backup key" = "新增備份金鑰";
"Require a physical key (plus your passphrase) to open this vault. Insert the new key and touch it twice to enrol." = "要求實體金鑰（外加你的密碼短語）來開啟此保險庫。插入新金鑰並輕觸兩次以完成註冊。";
"Enrol another key so any enrolled key opens this vault. Insert your current key and touch it, then swap to the new key and touch it twice. Keep the backup safe and separate — there's no recovery if you lose every key." = "註冊另一個金鑰，使任一已註冊金鑰都能開啟此保險庫。插入你當前的金鑰並輕觸，然後換上新金鑰並輕觸兩次。請將備份金鑰儲存在安全且獨立的地方——若丟失所有金鑰則沒有恢復。";
"Set/enter this key's PIN (leave blank if none)" = "設定/輸入此金鑰的 PIN 碼（若無則留空）";
"New key's PIN (leave blank if none)" = "新金鑰的 PIN 碼（若無則留空）";
"Name (optional)" = "名稱（可選）";
"Add key…" = "新增金鑰…";
"Add backup…" = "新增備份…";
"This vault already has the maximum of %lld keys." = "此保險庫已達到最多 %lld 個金鑰。";
"Working…" = "正在處理…";
"Follow the prompts on your key — insert, swap, and touch as asked. Don't unplug a key unless you're told to." = "按照金鑰上的提示操作——按要求插入、更換和輕觸。除非有提示，否則請勿拔下任何金鑰。";

