"Insert your YubiKey…" = "請插入你的 YubiKey…";
"Insert your CURRENT key (the one that already opens this vault)…" = "請插入你當前的金鑰（已經能開啟此保險庫的那個）…";
"Now insert the NEW backup key…" = "現在請插入新的備份金鑰…";
"Insert key %lld of %lld…" = "請插入第 %lld 個金鑰，共 %lld 個…";
"Insert the key you're removing…" = "請插入你要移除的金鑰…";
"Remove your current key, then insert the NEW backup key…" = "請拔下你當前的金鑰，然後插入新的備份金鑰…";
"Remove that key, then insert the next one…" = "請拔下該金鑰，然後插入下一個…";
" — touch %lld of %lld" = "——輕觸第 %lld 次，共 %lld 次";
"Key %lld of %lld: touch it now" = "第 %lld 個金鑰，共 %lld 個：現在輕觸它";
"Touch your YubiKey now" = "現在輕觸你的 YubiKey";
"Touch your CURRENT key now — not the new one yet" = "現在輕觸你當前的金鑰——先別碰新金鑰";
"Touch the new backup key now" = "現在輕觸新的備份金鑰";
"Touch the key to remove it" = "輕觸金鑰以移除它";

/* --- Key-operation status messages --- */
"Backup key enrolled. Either key now opens this vault — keep the backup somewhere safe and separate. There is still no recovery if you lose both." = "備份金鑰已註冊。現在任一金鑰都能開啟此保險庫——請將備份金鑰儲存在安全且獨立的地方。若兩個都丟失，仍然沒有恢復。";
"Backup key enrolled. Unlock again to continue." = "備份金鑰已註冊。請重新解鎖以繼續。";
"Could not add the backup key: %@. Your vault is unchanged." = "無法新增備份金鑰：%@。你的保險庫未更改。";
"Enter your passphrase to add a backup key." = "輸入你的密碼短語以新增備份金鑰。";
"Could not read keys: %@." = "無法讀取金鑰：%@。";
"Key revoked — it no longer opens this vault. Unlock again to continue." = "金鑰已吊銷——它不再開啟此保險庫。請重新解鎖以繼續。";
"Could not revoke the key: %@. Your vault is unchanged." = "無法吊銷該金鑰：%@。你的保險庫未更改。";
"Enter your passphrase to remove a key." = "輸入你的密碼短語以移除一個金鑰。";
"Enter your passphrase to remove the last key." = "輸入你的密碼短語以移除最後一個金鑰。";
"Last key removed. This vault now opens with the passphrase alone — and opening is slower again, by design." = "已移除最後一個金鑰。此保險庫現在僅憑密碼短語即可開啟——而開啟會再次變慢，出於設計。";
"Last key removed. Unlock again with your passphrase." = "已移除最後一個金鑰。請用你的密碼短語重新解鎖。";
"Could not remove the last key: %@. Your vault is unchanged." = "無法移除最後一個金鑰：%@。你的保險庫未更改。";

