"Removing the last key…" = "正在移除最後一個金鑰…";
"Enrolling your key…" = "正在註冊你的金鑰…";
"Creating vault…" = "正在建立保險庫…";
"Migrating… touch your YubiKey when it blinks." = "正在遷移…當 YubiKey 閃爍時請輕觸它。";

