"Re-encrypt this vault into a fresh file (new keys, or a smaller size). Used to rotate keys or upgrade the format. The original is kept until you confirm." = "將此保險庫重新加密到一個全新檔案（新金鑰，或更小的大小）。用於輪換金鑰或升級格式。在你確認之前會保留原檔案。";
