"Name, add, or revoke the hardware keys that open this vault (%lld of %lld enrolled), or convert back to passphrase-only." = "命名、新增或吊銷開啟此保險庫的硬體金鑰（已註冊 %lld 個，共 %lld 個），或恢復為僅密碼短語。";
"This vault has only one hardware key. Lose it and the vault is gone — enrol a backup key." = "此保險庫只有一個硬體金鑰。丟失它，保險庫就會丟失——請註冊一個備份金鑰。";
