/* --- File / folder dialogs --- */
"Delete this file?" = "刪除此檔案？";
"“%@” will be permanently removed and its encrypted chunks securely shredded. This cannot be undone — there is no recovery, by design." = "「%@」將被永久移除，其加密分塊將被安全粉碎。此操作無法撤銷——沒有恢復，出於設計。";
"Delete this folder?" = "刪除此資料夾？";
"“%@” and ALL its contents will be permanently removed and securely shredded. This cannot be undone." = "「%@」及其全部內容將被永久移除並安全粉碎。此操作無法撤銷。";
