"Create" = "建立";
"Rename file" = "重新命名檔案";
"Renaming “%@”. The encrypted content is unchanged; only the name in the manifest is updated." = "正在重新命名「%@」。加密內容不變；僅更新清單中的名稱。";
"New name" = "新名稱";

/* --- Import bar --- */
"New note" = "新建筆記";
"Create a new empty note and open it in the editor. It lives only inside the encrypted vault." = "建立一個新的空白筆記並在編輯器中開啟。它僅存在於加密保險庫內。";
"1 pass" = "1 遍";
"3 passes" = "3 遍";
"7 passes" = "7 遍";
"Overwrite passes. 1 is enough on any modern drive; 3/7 exist only for standards that mandate them and add nothing on an SSD." = "覆寫遍數。在任何現代驅動器上 1 遍即足夠；3/7 僅為強制要求的標準而存在，在 SSD 上沒有任何額外作用。";
"Shred originals" = "粉碎原件";
"After importing, securely overwrite and delete the source file. On a hard disk this physically erases it; on an SSD wear-leveling means it's best-effort only (no guarantee) — the real protection is the encrypted vault." = "匯入後，安全地覆寫並刪除原始檔。在硬碟上這會將其物理擦除；在 SSD 上，磨損均衡意味著這只是盡力而為（不保證）——真正的保護是加密保險庫。";
"Drag files here, or click Import. Files are encrypted into the vault; nothing is written elsewhere." = "將檔案拖到此處，或點選「匯入」。檔案將被加密到保險庫；不會在其他任何地方寫入內容。";
"Imported %lld; last error: %@" = "已匯入 %lld 個；最後一個錯誤：%@";
"Imported 1 file." = "已匯入 1 個檔案。";
"Imported %lld files." = "已匯入 %lld 個檔案。";
"Original securely erased (overwritten %lld× in place on a hard disk)." = "原件已安全擦除（在硬碟上原地覆寫 %lld 次）。";
"Original overwritten + deleted — but this is an SSD: wear-leveling means the cells may persist. The real protection is the encrypted vault, not the wipe." = "原件已覆寫並刪除——但這是 SSD：磨損均衡意味著單元可能仍然殘留。真正的保護是加密保險庫，而非擦除。";
"Original overwritten + deleted (storage type unknown; treated as flash — no physical-erase guarantee)." = "原件已覆寫並刪除（儲存型別未知；按快閃記憶體處理——不保證物理擦除）。";

/* --- File viewer --- */
"Save" = "儲存";
"Save the changes back into the encrypted vault. Nothing is written to disk." = "將更改儲存回加密保險庫。不會向磁碟寫入任何內容。";
"Edit" = "編輯";
"Edit this text file in the app and save it back into the vault. Nothing is written to disk." = "在應用內編輯此文字檔案並儲存回保險庫。不會向磁碟寫入任何內容。";
"Export…" = "匯出…";
"Write a decrypted copy of this file to disk, outside the vault. Shows a warning first." = "將此檔案的解密副本寫入磁碟，保險庫之外。會先顯示警告。";
"The vault isn’t open." = "保險庫未開啟。";

/* --- Export warning --- */
"Export a decrypted copy?" = "匯出解密副本？";
"You are about to write the decrypted contents of “%@” to a regular file on disk. Once written, that file leaves Farewell's protection:" = "你即將把「%@」的解密內容寫入磁碟上的普通檔案。一旦寫入，該檔案就離開了 Farewell 的保護：";
"Spotlight will index its contents" = "聚焦（Spotlight）會索引其內容";
"QuickLook will cache a thumbnail" = "快速檢視（QuickLook）會快取縮圖";
"Time Machine will back it up (if enabled)" = "時間機器（Time Machine）會備份它（若已啟用）";
"Apps that open it keep it in Recent Items" = "開啟它的應用會將其保留在「最近使用的專案」中";
"Farewell can no longer track or recall it" = "Farewell 將無法再跟蹤或召回它";
"Use the in-app viewer instead unless you genuinely need an external copy. For device-to-device transfer, Farewell-to-Farewell P2P (coming later) never writes cleartext to disk." = "除非你確實需要外部副本，否則請改用應用內檢視器。對於裝置間傳輸，Farewell 到 Farewell 的點對點功能（即將推出）絕不會向磁碟寫入明文。";
"Export anyway" = "仍然匯出";
"This file will be written UNENCRYPTED outside the vault." = "此檔案將以未加密形式寫入保險庫之外。";

/* --- Migrate sheet --- */
"Migrate / rotate vault" = "遷移 / 輪換保險庫";
"Re-encrypts everything into a brand-new vault file with fresh keys (the same passphrase). Your files are copied and verified before anything is replaced; nothing is written to disk in the clear. The original is kept until you delete it." = "將所有內容重新加密到一個全新的保險庫檔案中，使用新金鑰（相同的密碼短語）。在替換任何內容之前，你的檔案會被複制並驗證；不會以明文向磁碟寫入任何內容。在你刪除之前會保留原檔案。";
"New size" = "新大小";
"Keep current capacity" = "保持當前容量";
"Shrink to fit contents" = "收縮以適應內容";
"Destination:" = "目標位置：";
"Needs about %@; %@ free here." = "大約需要 %@；此處可用 %@。";
"This vault requires a YubiKey" = "此保險庫需要 YubiKey";
"Migrate" = "遷移";
"Use Folder" = "使用此資料夾";
"Not enough space on %@: the new vault needs about %@ but only %@ is free. Choose “Shrink to fit” or a different drive." = "%@ 上空間不足：新保險庫大約需要 %@，但僅有 %@ 可用。請選擇「收縮以適應內容」或其他驅動器。";
"A file named “%@” already exists in that folder. Pick another destination." = "該資料夾中已存在名為「%@」的檔案。請選擇其他目標位置。";
"Migration failed: %@. Your original vault is unchanged." = "遷移失敗：%@。你的原始保險庫未更改。";
"Migrated. The previous vault is kept as “%@” — delete it once you’ve confirmed this one works." = "已遷移。先前的保險庫保留為「%@」——確認此保險庫可用後請將其刪除。";
"Migrated to %@. Your original vault is unchanged — delete it when ready." = "已遷移到 %@。你的原始保險庫未更改——準備好後請將其刪除。";
"Migration verified but the file swap failed: %@. Your original vault is unchanged." = "遷移已驗證，但檔案交換失敗：%@。你的原始保險庫未更改。";

/* --- Create-vault rename notice --- */
"“%@” already existed — created “%@” instead. A vault is never overwritten." = "「%@」已存在——已改為建立「%@」。保險庫絕不會被覆蓋。";

