"About Farewell" = "關於 Farewell";
"sleep" = "睡眠";
"screen lock" = "鎖屏";
"inactivity" = "不活動";
"Vault locked automatically (%@). Unlock to continue." = "保險庫已自動鎖定（%@）。請解鎖以繼續。";

