/* --- Clé matérielle initiale + clarté clé de secours (ajout) --- */
"Adding a backup happens in two steps — and the order matters:" = "新增備份金鑰分兩步——順序很重要：";
"**1.** First insert your **current key** (the one that already opens this vault) and touch it — **not the new key yet**." = "**1.** 先插入你的**當前金鑰**（已經能開啟此保險庫的那個）並輕觸它——**先別碰新金鑰**。";
"**2.** Only then, when asked, swap to the **new backup key** and touch it twice." = "**2.** 然後在提示時，再換成**新的備份金鑰**並輕觸兩次。";
"Either key will then open the vault. Keep the backup somewhere safe and separate — there's no recovery if you lose every key." = "之後任一金鑰都能開啟此保險庫。請將備份金鑰儲存在安全且獨立的地方——若丟失所有金鑰，將無法恢復。";
"Enter your passphrase to add a hardware key." = "輸入你的密碼短語以新增硬體金鑰。";
"Adding your hardware key…" = "正在新增你的硬體金鑰…";
"Enrolling your hardware key…" = "正在註冊你的硬體金鑰…";
"Hardware key enrolled. This vault now needs that key plus your passphrase to open. Enrol a backup key too — lose your only key and the vault is gone, with no recovery." = "硬體金鑰已註冊。現在開啟此保險庫需要該金鑰加上你的密碼短語。也請註冊一個備份金鑰——若丟失唯一的金鑰，保險庫將丟失且無法恢復。";
"Hardware key enrolled. Unlock again to continue." = "硬體金鑰已註冊。請重新解鎖以繼續。";
"Could not add the hardware key: %@. Your vault is unchanged." = "無法新增硬體金鑰：%@。你的保險庫未更改。";
"Touch your new key now" = "現在輕觸你的新金鑰";
